ma-2-7b\\\").\\n- In code you can print model.config._name_or_path or the file/folder name of your weights.\\n\\n6) Third-party app or wrapped service\\n- Inspect the app settings, logs, or contact the app’s developer for which model they call.\\n\\nIf you tell me where/how you’re running it (ChatGPT UI, OpenAI API, local, third‑party app), paste the model name or the part of your request that sets \\\"model\\\", and I’ll confirm what version it is and what features you can expect.\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":1205,\"promptTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":1222}}}"}}
